          }
        },
        {
          "_comment": "Database Research Agent — escalation path for when the user's request is vague about which entities/fields are involved. ActionSmith should call this ONLY when Get Entity List + Get Entity Details aren't enough (e.g., 'build an action that analyzes customer revenue' when revenue could live on Orders, Invoices, LineItems, or a view). DRA runs open-ended SQL exploration and returns a synthesized schema summary. SubAgentOutputMapping pulls its findings into ActionSmith's payload under `schemaResearch` so ActionSmith can reference them when defining the contract.",
          "fields": {
